      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the S54-powered legend. The 3.2L high-revving straight-six features a double-VANOS system that remains in peak operational spec, delivering linear power through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. The chassis has undergone proactive rear subframe reinforcement, and the factory-spec limited-slip differential provides exceptional corner-exit traction. This unit retains its original factory paint with zero swirl marks and an interior free of bolster wear or dash UV damage. Mechanical sympathy is evident throughout, with a documented history of valve adjustments and rod bearing service. A true investment-grade specimen for the discerning collector.",
